CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, pg. A17, reads: "Models Rehearse - Models who will take part in the fabulous Beauty Shop Owners fashion show, April 30, at Schenley High School, are shown as they head for rehearsals.  Bottom to top of stairs are Jessie Middlebrook, Mackie Woodson, Martha Lucke, Sydney Taylor Brown, Sadie Robinson, Edward Tyler, Donald Flanagan and Donald Hunt. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Jessie Middlebrook, Mackie Woodson, Martha Lucke, Sydney Taylor Brown, Sadie Robinson, Edward Tyler, Donald Flanagan, and Donald Hunt holding Las Vegas banner and standing on steps of Centre Avenue YMCA
